ActsAsOrg
==========

Provides org-mode actions for ActiveFile records.  See the following
for information on the relevant resources.

- active file
- org-mode

Installation
============

From the root of your rails project execute the following

> ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/eschulte/acts_as_org.git

This plugin requires

Requires:
- Emacs22 or later (preferably Emacs 23) (see [Emacs](http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/))
- ActiveFile (see [ActiveFile on github](http://github.com/eschulte/active_file/tree/master))

